Title: TICINO Type-A B-URH Pilot Watch Miyota 9015 movement
Description: You are viewing a... TICINO Type-A B-URH Pilot Watch This wonderfully finished case is now housing a top grade Miyota 9015 movement. This is a 24 jewel with high beat rate which keeps extremely accurate time. This upgraded Ticino still has a double dome sapphire crystal which covers a really crisp superlume dial. The hands are blue and have also been applied with super luminova. Soft strap and deployment buckle and metal rivets reminiscent of Burh watches long ago. Ticino still tries to provide customer with unbeatable deals keeping the prices low and not sacrificing quality. WATCH FEATURES 316L stainless steel case All brushed satin finish case Diameter: 44mm, 48mm including crown, and 13.8mm thick 10 ATM water resistant Double Domed Sapphire crystal (scratch proof) Solid Screw down case back with O-ring gasket for water protection Black Brown Calfskin strap with signed deployment buckle. Fits 9 inch wrist, lug width 20mm Automatic Miyota 9015 24 jewels, high beat rate 28,800 bph, the movement hacks and can be hand wound. Made In Japan Movement holder metal Dial black with Swiss C1 SuperLuminova Hands with navy blue trim with Swiss C1 SuperLuminova Comes with a Warranty Card and Presentation Box (box design may vary) WE ARE PAYPAL VERIFIED | HAPPY SHOPPING !!!
